== Restauro 25/04/2015

Comandi utili:

    rvm rubygems 1.4.1 --force
    sudo apt-get install imagemagick libmagickcore-dev libmagickwand-dev

    mysql -uroot -p
        create database filo_production;
        grant all on filo_production.* to 'filo'@localhost identified by '....';

    gunzip < $dump | mysql -ufilo -p filo_production


